%h3 Common Issues
%p I've got a lot of great feedback from some people, and there are a few problems that have been raised. Here's some common solutions:
%ul.issues
  %li
    %p 
      %b Q: It crashes on Windows sometimes.
      %br
      A: Try installing to C:\apps. This has fixed crashes for some users.
  %li
    %p 
      %b Q: I just get a bunch of boxes on the opening Screen!
      %br
      A: Make sure you drag it out of the .dmg and onto your computer.
  %li
    %p 
      %b Q: The icon bounces once, and then doesn't open!
      %br
      A: Make sure you're using OSX 10.6, on a 64 bit machine. Others coming soon!
  %li
    %p 
      %b Q: On Ubuntu, I get an error about libssh2
      %br
      A: Try sudo apt-get install libssh2-1. Sorry about that!
%p I am currently working to resolve all of these issues. Please <a href="/stream">let me know</a> if you have any other problems. I'll be releasing updated versions on a regular basis.
